### Google Custom Search API - Test Requests
### Use this file with the REST Client extension in VS Code

### Variables
@apimGatewayUrl = https://YOUR-APIM-GATEWAY.azure-api.net
@subscriptionKey = YOUR-SUBSCRIPTION-KEY
@searchEngineId = YOUR-SEARCH-ENGINE-ID

### ==========================================================================
### Test 1: Basic Search Query
### ==========================================================================
GET {{apimGatewayUrl}}/google-search/?q=Azure%20API%20Management&cx={{searchEngineId}}
api-key: {{subscriptionKey}}

### ==========================================================================
### Test 2: Search with Number of Results
### ==========================================================================
GET {{apimGatewayUrl}}/google-search/?q=Citadel%20AI%20Gateway&cx={{searchEngineId}}&num=5
api-key: {{subscriptionKey}}

### ==========================================================================
### Test 3: Paginated Search (start from result 11)
### ==========================================================================
GET {{apimGatewayUrl}}/google-search/?q=Azure%20OpenAI&cx={{searchEngineId}}&num=10&start=11
api-key: {{subscriptionKey}}

### ==========================================================================
### Test 4: Complex Query with URL Encoding
### ==========================================================================
GET {{apimGatewayUrl}}/google-search/?q=how%20to%20deploy%20Azure%20Functions&cx={{searchEngineId}}
api-key: {{subscriptionKey}}

### ==========================================================================
### Test 5: Missing Required Parameter 'q' (should return 400)
### ==========================================================================
GET {{apimGatewayUrl}}/google-search/?cx={{searchEngineId}}
api-key: {{subscriptionKey}}

### ==========================================================================
### Test 6: Missing Required Parameter 'cx' (should return 400)
### ==========================================================================
GET {{apimGatewayUrl}}/google-search/?q=test
api-key: {{subscriptionKey}}

### ==========================================================================
### Test 7: Without Subscription Key (should return 401)
### ==========================================================================
GET {{apimGatewayUrl}}/google-search/?q=test&cx={{searchEngineId}}

### ==========================================================================
